	   <tr><td colspan=2>My suggestion would be to stick to root. I'm a 38 and half season wiz and of all the spells to hold mobs root is so far the best now even though it still gets resisted it still works best. My suggestion would be to try this tactic&nbsp;&nbsp;Tashan clash (stun), Root and then DD. I have found that if tashan clash is not resisted your root tends to stick a little better.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
