	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am lvl 36 and I totally disagree.&nbsp;&nbsp;My root rarely holds (enstill or root either one).  I pull with Bonds of Force, if resisted I back up until I can recast and cast Tashan's Clash.  I then back up and recast my Bonds of Force.  Very rarely does the second Bonds get resisted.  I then merrily kite away until said mob is dead.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
