	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm a lvl 46 wiz currently fighting in Burning Woods (soloing) although we wizards can demolish a mob in sec we have some slight drawbacks low armor and our root spell which is suppose to keep mobs off of you breaks alot. My suggestion as i have had to change my tactics is to go with bonds of force to kite your mob and if you don't have Jboots atleast be sowed also after using bonds of force you can try rooting the mob which i have had good success with. Well good luck and happy hunting.<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;                                         PS If you go to BW and want to solo unless you have a group or are using one of the best nukes (Ice Comet) don't solo the Wurms. I would swear they have atleast 7K hps. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
